beer.beer_description:
Way back in the Winter of 2011 we released Pulse. The beautiful marriage of hops and oatmeal with a Belgian yeast. Pulse (Belgian Oatmeal IPA) was extremely well received even though it was ahead of its time. Using this as inspiration we've revitalised it in a Pale Ale guise.

Luscious in colour and mouth-feel with assertive bitterness and complexity from the Belgian yeast this Pale Ale has the Doctor's Orders twist.

Malts: Ale, Wheat, Oats, Munich and Light Crystal

Hops: Target, Chinook, Citra and Amarillo

Yeast: Belgian Saison
